tag.name: would have been better without the rapping

wiki.summary: “golden hour” is the third song released off of JVKE’s debut album. Before announcing the title and pre-save link, JVKE shared on his Instagram story on July 12, 2022: "This song has a special place in my heart and I can’t wait to share it with you all. I did my absolute best to embody beauty in every detail of the production." Read more on Last.fm.
